## Deferred to a future plan (NOT this round)

The entire **backend realization** — flovenet-native implementation (4 derived facets, native circles via OR-Set CRDT + forward-secret group keys, native invite/lineage module, presence, follows-as-mirror, native AI) and the **oasis add-on** (SSB federation bridge, "42" pluggable engine) — is specified in `…-vs-flovenet-oasis-comparison.md` and becomes its own plan. The MyWizy inference-engine details (local vs shared-mesh, pluggable backend) are explicitly further-spec-later.

## Out of scope (per spec §13)

Real auth/keypair crypto/backend/persisted stars (all mock, reset on reload); persisting unlock state into `apps/index.html`; finalizing trust-score weights; abuse adjudication flow; new fonts/hues on nety; profily/sety internal refactors beyond the listed items.
